 |title=Capturing nuclear whistle-blower was 'a lucky stroke,' agents recall
 |publisher=[[Ha'aretz]]
 |date=[[November 12]] [[2006]]
}}</ref>and by others as a [[treason|traitor]].<ref>{{cite web
