He has been highly critical of Israel's political actions, refuses to speak [[Hebrew language|Hebrew]]{{Fact|date=May 2007}}, and rejects the need for a [[Jewish state]] to exist.<ref name=Vanunu_defiant>{{cite news
 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/3640989.stm
